room_title: Escape room "Presidential Assassination" by Time Escape in Seattle
room_description:
The day has come for the inauguration ceremony. However, the government’s protective services have been tipped off the plans of an assassination, putting the president’s life on the line. It has been revealed that one of our secret agents has recently joined an infamous terrorist organization, fighting to throw the country into chaos.
Your job is to seek out this double agent, find the information to prove him guilty and wipe him out before the assassination takes place. The time machine can only send you within the 45 minutes before the terrorist pulls the trigger, so it's you and your team’s race against time to save your president, along with your country!
